How It Works
Reset Button:

Pauses both timers using pauseTimer.
Resets their values to 60.
Sends updates to display.html to reflect the changes immediately.
User Experience:

Pressing the reset button stops any running timer and resets both displays to 60.
Result
A "Reset Both Timers" button is added to the controls page.
Resetting works seamlessly without disrupting the real-time updates to the display page.